234
00:15:43,977 --> 00:15:49,816
Pink Sugar Heart Attack!

235
00:15:51,117 --> 00:15:52,986
[grunt]

236
00:15:53,319 --> 00:15:55,155
Get away from Mommy Ikuko!

237
00:15:55,288 --> 00:15:55,956
