238
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:59,159
Yeah, "Mommy!" 'Cuz she's my
mommy in this world!

239
00:16:00,426 --> 00:16:03,103
So, keep your grubby hands off
her, you big creep!

240
00:16:03,604 --> 00:16:05,171
Yeah, you tell him!

241
00:16:05,338 --> 00:16:07,407
Annoying little runt!...[grunt]

242
00:16:07,508 --> 00:16:08,842
[groan]

243
00:16:08,975 --> 00:16:09,510
(Usagi) [groan]

244
00:16:09,643 --> 00:16:10,944
Sailor Moon!

245
00:16:11,011 --> 00:16:12,979
Come on! We'll save mom
together!

246
00:16:13,079 --> 00:16:13,514
Hm!

247
00:16:16,182 --> 00:16:16,583
[grunt]

248
00:16:37,437 --> 00:16:45,145
Moon Spiral Heart Attack!

249
