No way!

251
00:16:54,187 --> 00:16:57,223
My turn!...

252
00:16:58,024 --> 00:16:59,392
[screams]

253
00:16:59,492 --> 00:17:00,393
[gasps]

254
00:17:00,493 --> 00:17:01,334
[high‐pitch twittering]

255
