261
00:17:21,254 --> 00:17:26,527
[groans]

262
00:17:29,896 --> 00:17:31,097
Come on, we can't give up!

263
00:17:31,565 --> 00:17:33,934
[groan]

264
00:17:35,101 --> 00:17:39,439
