266
00:17:48,949 --> 00:17:52,919
<i>(Pegasus) Only you, who</i>
<i>possesses a heart willing to</i>
<i>protect beautiful dreams, can</i>
<i>summon me...</i>

267
00:17:53,019 --> 00:17:55,455
