<i>these words: "Moon Crisis Make</i>
<i>Up."</i>

272
00:18:14,114 --> 00:18:17,150
Sailor Moon! We have to shout,
"Moon Crisis Make Up!"

273
00:18:17,283 --> 00:18:18,084
We do? Why?

274
00:18:18,151 --> 00:18:19,152
Never mind, just do it!

275
00:18:21,622 --> 00:18:25,892
<i>Moon Crisis Make Up!</i>

276
00:18:58,024 --> 00:18:59,159
Great, now what?!

277
00:18:59,259 --> 00:19:00,867
[gasps]

278
00:19:02,803 --> 00:19:07,874
<i>(Pegasus) Take these. They are</i>
<i>your new powers...The Kaleido</i>
<i>Moon Scope and Crystal Carillon.</i>

279
00:19:08,609 --> 00:19:11,144
<i>Now,...call out my name!</i>

280
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:17,818
Please, Pegasus!...Protect
everyone's dream!

281
00:19:21,555 --> 00:19:24,057
Twinkle Yell!

282
00:19:29,395 --> 00:19:33,399
