these brats...[grunt]

289
00:20:35,068 --> 00:20:41,074
<i>(Pegasus) Henceforth, whenever</i>
<i>you need my power, just hold up</i>
<i>the Crystal Carillon and call my</i>
<i>name.</i>

290
00:20:43,243 --> 00:20:44,144
Pegasus...

291
00:20:45,211 --> 00:20:46,547
