292
00:20:48,414 --> 00:20:49,415
[sigh]

293
00:20:51,585 --> 00:20:53,754
<i>(Rei) Wow, it looks delicious!</i>

294
00:20:53,887 --> 00:20:54,320
<i>(Usagi) I'll say!</i>

295
00:20:55,021 --> 00:20:55,421
(Mamoru) Smells delicious, too!

296
00:20:55,989 --> 00:20:56,422
(Ami) Thank you so much!

297
00:20:57,023 --> 00:20:58,091
I hope you all like it.

298
00:20:58,191 --> 00:20:59,225
Thank you!

299
